---
title: Very Merry Cheesy Maple Bacon Burger Beef Burger, Fig Jam, Goat's Cheese, Maple Bacon Wedges and Balsamic Salad
description: Serve up a festive feast this winter! Super indulgent and packed full of flavour, this Very Merry Cheesy Maple Bacon Burger is your favourite burger brought to the next level.
